* ISO 20022\nCollateral Management (colr)
** Purpose
*** Mitigate counterparty credit risk
*** OTC derivatives, repo, sec lending
*** CSA / ISDA, UMR margin rules
** Concepts
*** Variation margin (VM)
*** Initial margin (IM)\nSegregated Independent Amount
*** Threshold and MTA
*** Haircut
*** Eligible collateral
** Bilateral messages
*** 001/002 Collateral Value Query/Report
*** 003/004 Margin Call Request/Response
*** 009 Margin Call Dispute
*** 007/008 Collateral Proposal/Response
*** 010/011/012 Substitution
*** 013/014/015 Interest Payment
*** 016 Collateral and Exposure Report
*** 005/006 Cancellation Request/Status
** Triparty messages
*** 019 Transaction Instruction
*** 020 Processing Status Advice
*** 021 Allegement Notification
*** 022 Collateral and Exposure Report
*** 023 Status Advice
*** 024 Allegement Cancellation
*** reda.074 Unilateral Removal
** Actors
*** Two counterparties
*** Triparty agent (custodian/CSD)
